					},
					"name": "Terran Physiology",
					"local_notes": "You can always be stronger, you can always be faster, you can always be better. You may purchase all attributes at a cheaper price than normal. Your specific race may change these values, but will always be affected by this trait regardless. This does not reduce the cost of any Advantages.",
